snippet.title: RAGE 2 - Open World Trailer
snippet.description:
The wasteland of RAGE 2 is your playground – your very bloody playground –and in a world where there are no rules, insanity rules. Go anywhere, shoot anything, explode everything. RAGE 2 will be available on PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC on May 14, 2019. 

Get a fresh look at the chaotic and crazy world in the latest trailer.

RAGE 2 is coming to PlayStation 4, Xbox One and PC on May 14, 2019. Pre-order to receive the exclusive Cult of the Death God mission and don Nicholas Raine’s legendary armor and Settler Pistol. 

The RAGE 2 Collector’s Edition is also available for pre-order. Get the full breakdown of all the included goodies on RAGE.com.

For more information on RAGE 2, follow these channels: 

Website – https://beth.games/rage
Facebook – https://facebook.com/rage
Twitter – https://twitter.com/rage
Instagram – https://instagram.com/rage
